Package swen221.cardgame.cards.core

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CardGame
    Represents a Whist-like card game.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Card  
    Hand
    Represents a hand of cards held by a player.
    Player
    Represents a player on the board, which can be either a computer player or a human.
    Trick
    Represents a trick being played.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Card.Rank
    Represents the different card "numbers".
    Card.Suit
    Represents a card suit.
    Player.Direction
    Represents one of the four position on the table (North, East, South and West).
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    IllegalMove
    Use to signal an illegal move has occurred.
